The Hollywood Ten in November 1947 waiting to be fingerprinted in the <a href="/wiki/U.S._Marshal" title="U.S. Marshal" class="mw-redirect">U.S. Marshal</a>'s office after being cited for <a href="/wiki/Contempt_of_Congress" title="Contempt of Congress">contempt of Congress</a>. Front row (from left): <a href="/wiki/Herbert_Biberman" title="Herbert Biberman">Herbert Biberman</a>, attorneys Martin Popper and <a href="/wiki/Robert_W._Kenny" title="Robert W. Kenny">Robert W. Kenny</a>, <a href="/wiki/Albert_Maltz" title="Albert Maltz">Albert Maltz</a>, <a href="/wiki/Lester_Cole" title="Lester Cole">Lester Cole</a>. Middle row: <a href="/wiki/Dalton_Trumbo" title="Dalton Trumbo">Dalton Trumbo</a>, <a href="/wiki/John_Howard_Lawson" title="John Howard Lawson">John Howard Lawson</a>, <a href="/wiki/Alvah_Bessie" title="Alvah Bessie" class="mw-redirect">Alvah Bessie</a>, <a href="/wiki/Samuel_Ornitz" title="Samuel Ornitz">Samuel Ornitz</a>. Back row: <a href="/wiki/Ring_Lardner_Jr." title="Ring Lardner Jr." class="mw-redirect">Ring Lardner Jr.</a>, <a href="/wiki/Edward_Dmytryk" title="Edward Dmytryk">Edward Dmytryk</a>, <a href="/wiki/Adrian_Scott" title="Adrian Scott">Adrian Scott</a>.</div>
